# ============================================================
# HOW EMAIL SERVICE CHOOSES PROVIDER:
# ============================================================
# Priority order:
# 1. RESEND_API_KEY set → Use Resend API ← RECOMMENDED
# 2. EMAIL_PASSWORD set → Use Gmail SMTP ← Fallback
# 3. Neither set → Development mode (logs OTP to console)


